Interface Wrapper<T>

  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface Wrapper<T>
    Marker interface for types that "wrap" some other objects. By means of this interface it is possible to wrap and unwrap objects with a given instance without knowing the actual implementing java type.
